from cfnlint.config import ConfigMixIn

# Create a basic configuration for the Runner
class BasicConfig(ConfigMixIn):
    def __init__(self):
        super().__init__()
        self.templates = []
        self.append_rules = []
        self.custom_rules = ""
        self.override_spec = ""
        self.registry_schemas = []
        self.ignore_bad_template = False
        self.ignore_checks = []
        self.include_checks = []
        self.mandatory_checks = []
        self.non_zero_exit_code = "error"
        self.format = "json"
        self.build_graph = False
        self.update_specs = False
        self.update_iam_policies = False
        self.update_documentation = False
        self.listrules = False
        self.debug = False
        self.info = False
        self.output_file = None
        self.force = False

config = BasicConfig()
